QuestData.Title: Dangerous State
QuestData.Description:
Enemies have attacked the jiro and severed them from the circle. The jiro are no longer stable. They are a danger to the order of things.
They must be removed.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: A cruel and manipulative follower of Zovaal.
QuestData.LogDescription: Leashkeeper Helzid and $1oa Dominated Jiro slain
QuestData.RewardText: Order has been restored. Thank you for your assistance.
